Class CHIAAutomataConsole

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.console.CHIAAutomataConsole

  • public class CHIAAutomataConsole
extends Object
    Is the Console associated with the automata mode. It specifies the set of action that can be performed when the automata mode is selected
    Author:
    Claudio Menghi
